            {
               "text": "<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><b><a href=\"index.html?page=class_content&arg=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">Volume 1 – The Foundations of the Universe</a></b>: In this volume, we study, through different cultures, how we discovered the numbers we use in our daily lives and explore their use in different stages of our life.</p><p style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><b><a href=\"index.html?page=class_content&arg=first_steps_volume2\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps_volume2','html', '', false); return false;\">Volume 2 – Within Our Reach</a></b>: In this volume, we study and deepen our knowledge about numbers, expanding our perspective into the heart of different cultures.</p>",
